{
  "stem": "19210.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, to me, my wife's family and to be with her family, because in, in Israel, of course, I had a brother and a cousin.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later on, two sisters came to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I love Israel, but I didn't have as many opportunities to advance in life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought I was given an opportunity by my cousins, my wife's cousins.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I felt that it was my duty then to give my children also an opportunity to advance in life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think I had done my share, even though one never really fulfills really given share to the community, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I decided that we're going to give it a try and come to America.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We like America.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we're very happy to be here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, always, always-- I always communicated with, primarily with my, with my Aunt Esther, because she had the most beautiful handwriting.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I loved to read her letters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She read-- wrote beautiful Portuguese.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had some letters, of course, from my father and my mother as well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But some from the family-- a large family-- but we always communicated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I came to visit them about 15 years later after I had left, and I brought my wife and three children, I think we had a hero's welcome.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the whole community was very happy to see us and welcomed us, as well as my family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Perhaps a little bit better, but not by much, my immediate family-- some, some of my family was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sisters, they married not within the faith.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there was no Jewish youth in Portugal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was one of the main reasons, too, that I left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and my brothers also married not within the faith.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
